This project shall always remain FREE for everyone.

Commercial use of this project, in whole or in part, is STRICTLY PROHIBITED.

The following actions are NOT permitted:

• Selling the original project.
• Selling modified versions.
• Selling source code.
• Selling compiled binaries.
• Selling firmware based on this project.
• Selling educational packages primarily containing this project.
• Selling training material whose primary value comes from this project.
• Including this project in commercial software.
• Including this project in commercial hardware products.
• Charging money for copies or downloads of this project.
• Charging money for access to this project.

No person or organization may directly or indirectly profit from the
distribution of this project.

Commercial use requires prior written permission from the copyright owner.

